## Model routing (parent / Task tool)

When the **Task** tool exposes a `model` parameter (or equivalent), prefer this routing. **Subagent YAML `model:` is not authoritative** (see above).

| Task type | Model tier | Reason |
| --------- | ---------- | ------ |
| Explore / recon subagents | **fast** | Read-only; speed matters |
| Build subagents (clear spec) | **fast** | Implementation with bounded scope |
| Documentation / boilerplate | **fast** | Lower risk |
| Security review | **strongest available** | Risk-sensitive |
| Architect / staff-level review | **strongest available** | Complex tradeoffs |
| Fix-loop iteration **3+** | **strongest available** | Deeper reasoning when stuck |

If only one alias is offered, still delegate for isolation; accept product constraints.

